DBIx-MySperqlOO version 1.0.0
=====================

MySperqlOO enables sql statement execution (through DBI to MySQL) 
with one line of perl code. Enhanced for OO from DBIx-MySperql.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  MySQL Server

  DBI
  DBD::mysql
  Class::Std
  Class::Std::Utils

